headline: RMD Q2 Deep Dive: Margin Expansion and Product Innovation Drive Outperformance
summary: Medical device company ResMed (NYSE:RMD) reported Q2 CY2025 results beating Wall Street’s revenue expectations, with sales up 10.2% year on year to $1.35 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $2.55 per share was 3% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
